title: december 12: to the depths of antarctica
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the deepest point on earth, and then about the continent, Antarctica, that holds it. Then, she talks about a funny high school prank that raised money for charity. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
